snippet.title: Godzilla x Kong : The New Empire | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Witness the rise of a new empire. #GodzillaXKong - Only in theaters 2024

The epic battle continues!  Legendary Pictures‚Äô cinematic Monsterverse follows up the explosive showdown of ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù with an all-new adventure that pits the almighty Kong and the fearsome Godzilla against a colossal undiscovered threat hidden within our world, challenging their very existence‚Äîand our own. ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire‚Äù delves further into the histories of these Titans and their origins, as well as the mysteries of Skull Island and beyond, while uncovering the mythic battle that helped forge these extraordinary beings and tied them to humankind forever.

Once again at the helm is director Adam Wingard.  The film stars Rebecca Hall (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù The Night House‚Äù), Brian Tyree Henry (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúBullet Train‚Äù), Dan Stevens (‚ÄúGaslit,‚Äù ‚ÄúLegion,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast‚Äù), Kaylee Hottle (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù), Alex Ferns (‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù ‚ÄúWrath of Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúChernobyl‚Äù) and Fala Chen (‚ÄúIrma Vep,‚Äù ‚ÄúShang Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings‚Äù).

The screenplay is by Terry Rossio (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù the ‚ÄúPirates of the Caribbean‚Äù series) and Simon Barrett (‚ÄúYou‚Äôre Next‚Äù) and Jeremy Slater (‚ÄúMoon Knight‚Äù), from a story by Rossio & Wingard & Barrett, based on the character ‚ÄúGodzilla‚Äù owned and created by TOHO Co., Ltd..  The film is produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric Mcleod, Thomas Tull, Jon Jashni and Brian Rogers.  The executive producers are Wingard, Jen Conroy, Jay Ashenfelter, Yoshimitsu Banno, Kenji Okuhira. 

Once again, Wingard is collaborating with director of photography Ben Seresin (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúWorld War Z‚Äù), production designer Tom Hammock (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúX,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Guest‚Äù), editor Josh Schaeffer (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMolly‚Äôs Game‚Äù), costume designer Emily Seresin (‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúTop of the Lake‚Äù).  The composers are Tom Holkenborg (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù) and Antonio Di Iorio (additional music on ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù the ‚ÄúSonic the Hedgehog‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire.‚Äù  It is slated for release nationwide only in theaters and IMAX on April 12, 2024 and beginning 10 April 2024 internationally, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures except in Japan, where the film will be distributed by Toho Co., Ltd and in mainland China, where it will be distributed by Legendary East.

Legendary Pictures‚Äô cinematic Monsterverse follows up the explosive showdown of ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù with an all-new adventure that pits the almighty Kong and the fearsome Godzilla against a colossal undiscovered threat hidden within our world, challenging their very existence‚Äîand our own. ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire‚Äù delves further into the histories of these Titans and their origins, as well as the mysteries of Skull Island and beyond, while uncovering the mythic battle that helped forge these extraordinary beings and tied them to humankind forever.

Once again at the helm is director Adam Wingard.  The film stars Rebecca Hall (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù The Night House‚Äù), Brian Tyree Henry (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúBullet Train‚Äù), Dan Stevens (‚ÄúGaslit,‚Äù ‚ÄúLegion,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast‚Äù), Kaylee Hottle (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù), Alex Ferns (‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù ‚ÄúWrath of Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúChernobyl‚Äù) and Fala Chen (‚ÄúIrma Vep,‚Äù ‚ÄúShang Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings‚Äù).

The screenplay is by Terry Rossio (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong‚Äù the ‚ÄúPirates of the Caribbean‚Äù series) and Simon Barrett (‚ÄúYou‚Äôre Next‚Äù) and Jeremy Slater (‚ÄúMoon Knight‚Äù), from a story by Rossio & Wingard & Barrett, based on the character ‚ÄúGodzilla‚Äù owned and created by TOHO Co., Ltd..  The film is produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric Mcleod, Thomas Tull, Jon Jashni and Brian Rogers.  The executive producers are Wingard, Jen Conroy, Jay Ashenfelter, Yoshimitsu Banno, Kenji Okuhira. 

Once again, Wingard is collaborating with director of photography Ben Seresin (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúWorld War Z‚Äù), production designer Tom Hammock (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúX,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Guest‚Äù), editor Josh Schaeffer (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMolly‚Äôs Game‚Äù), costume designer Emily Seresin (‚ÄúThe Invisible Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúTop of the Lake‚Äù).  The composers are Tom Holkenborg (‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù ‚ÄúMad Max: Fury Road‚Äù) and Antonio Di Iorio (additional music on ‚ÄúGodzilla vs. Kong,‚Äù the ‚ÄúSonic the Hedgehog‚Äù films).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, ‚ÄúGodzilla x Kong: The New Empire.‚Äù  It is slated for release nationwide only in theaters and IMAX on April 12, 2024 and beginning 10 April 2024 internationally, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures except in Japan, where the film will be distributed by Toho Co., Ltd and in mainland China, where it will be distributed by Legendary East.

snippet.description:
Please‚Ä¶I‚Ä¶Kindly‚Ä¶Request!üî•
Presenting the Trailer of #SalaarCeaseFire


From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

Presenting the Trailer of #SalaarCeaseFire


From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Dec 22, 2023.

snippet.title: New Update - Town Hall 16 in Clash of Clans!
snippet.description:
TH16 Update Sneak Peek for Clash of Clans! Judo Sloth Gaming shares Town Hall 16 Gameplay as well as information on New Troop and Defense Levels coming in the update. There are numerous building upgrades shared alongside Balance Changes, Cost Reductions and the ability to finally attack your own base! snippet.title: Dating Mausi Ki Student - Stand Up Comedy by Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi (Crowd Work Video)
snippet.description:
Hello Doston,

Presenting a new Stand Up Comedy crowd work video:
Dating Mausi Ki Student which was recorded in my comedy show called BEST OF GUPTAJI.

This is a New Stand Up Comedy video which we have recorded in October at The Comedy Theatre, Gurgoan

Hope you enjoy this latest comedy video. 

And Yes, After a wild tour of Kaafi Wild Hai and Genuinely, I am presenting my new show with an old name Best of GuptaJi which I am starting to tour now.
Why Best of GuptaJi? because I want all the content in my show to be the best content from my side. So if you have seen my videos on chai, maggi, hotel, airport, tinder, starbucks etc, it was a part of Best of GuptaJi only so am trying to give you new content but with that level only.

If you want to come for the Best of GuptaJi tour, here is the ticket link : https://linktr.ee/appurvgupta

Book Now as we have limited seats in every city.

Thank You for watching Videos of Indian Stand Up Comedian Appurv Gupta aka GuptaJi.

For LIVE SHOWS Booking, Email: teamguptaji@gmail.com 

If Want to see more videos, Click here: https://goo.gl/rZA68k

3 Star Guide for the Last TH15 Challenge in Clash of Clans! Town Hall 16 has been confirmed for the December Update. This CoC Event attack gives one final challenge at Town Hall 15 where we replicate a 3 Star Attack from the World Champions. Since TH15 was a difficult meta this one is tricky, especially if you're not a TH15 player, however you get unlimited tries so I'm sure you will get this. Best of luck. Clash On!

snippet.title: 99 Details From the GTA 6 Trailer
snippet.description:
Don't miss our GTA 6 trailer breakdown! The GTA 6 trailer is finally here and we've looked over the entire footage and uncovered 99 hidden and hard to find details littered throughout our first look at GTA VI.

There are lots of cool new things to pick out from this brand new Grand Theft Auto 6 trailer from Rockstar Games, and in our GTA 6 trailer deep dive, we examine clues about GTA 6 map locations, hints about the GTA 6 world, glimpses of what might happen in the GTA 6 story, references to GTA Vice City, and more.

The GTA 6 release date is 2025 on PS5 and Xbox Series X/S.

Credit to tachyon_v for the map creation 

For more on Grand Theft Auto VI, check out our GTA 6 trailer reaction video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PuMSEkVqC9k

Episode 3946: Daya Ka Intezaar
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jethalal discovers that he has been lying about Daya's homecoming, he strikes Sundar with a bamboo stick. Sundar runs, but Jetha pursues after him. Champaklal shouts at Sundar and admits that Daya did not return because her mother did not want her to leave the house during the auspicious Diwali season. Later, Jethalal and Tapu inquire about Daya's ultimate arrival date with Sundar.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3946, 5 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: CID cast Shivaji Satam, Aditya Srivastava at crematorium for last rites of late actor Dinesh Phadnis
snippet.description:
CID cast members Shivaji Satam, Aditya Srivastava, Tanya Abrol, and Ansha Sayed gathered at the crematorium to pay their respects to the late actor Dinesh Phadnis, who passed away last night. His last rites took place at Daulat Nagar crematorium in Borivali around 10:30-11 am. The actor, who battled for his life, succumbed around 12 am after being admitted to Tunga Hospital in Mumbai. --------------------------------------------------------

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayali's by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayali's. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Daya is worried for her brother when he doesn't answer her call. Meanwhile, Bapuji scolds Jethalal for waking up late in the morning and asks him to get up early to go to the park for a walk.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Episode No - 472

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.description:
